# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NCR REAL ESTATE CHATBOT — API KEYS TEMPLATE
#
# HOW TO USE THIS FILE:
#   1. Make a copy of this file and name it exactly:  .env
#   2. Fill in your actual API keys below (replace the placeholder text)
#   3. NEVER share your .env file or upload it to GitHub
#      (it is already listed in .gitignore so Git will ignore it)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── ANTHROPIC API KEY ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This key lets the app talk to Claude Haiku (the AI brain of the chatbot).
# Used in: Step 2 (understanding the question) and Step 4 (formatting the answer)
#
# How to get it:
#   1. Go to https://console.anthropic.com
#   2. Sign up / log in
#   3. Click "API Keys" in the left menu
#   4. Click "Create Key" and copy it here
#
# Cost: New accounts get ~$5 free credits. At Haiku's rate, this covers
#       500+ full conversations — more than enough for this project.
#
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here


# ── SEARCHAPI KEYS (one per team member) ─────────────────────────────────────
# SearchAPI fetches live Google Search results for property listings.
# Used in: Step 3 (searching for real data — no AI involved here)
#
# How to get it:
#   1. Go to https://www.searchapi.io
#   2. Sign up for a FREE account (each account gets 100 free searches)
#   3. Copy your API key from the dashboard
#
# KEY ROTATION: The code automatically switches to the next key when one
# runs out of searches. 4 members × 100 searches = 400 combined searches.
#
SEARCHAPI_KEY_1=your_searchapi_key_1_here
SEARCHAPI_KEY_2=your_searchapi_key_2_here
SEARCHAPI_KEY_3=your_searchapi_key_3_here
SEARCHAPI_KEY_4=your_searchapi_key_4_here
